# act configuration for local GitHub Actions testing
# https://nektosact.com/

# Use full GitHub runner image (has rustup, cargo, etc pre-installed)
# Options:
#   catthehacker/ubuntu:act-latest (~500MB, minimal)
#   catthehacker/ubuntu:full-latest (~12GB, full GitHub runner with most tools)
-P ubuntu-latest=catthehacker/ubuntu:full-latest

# For Apple Silicon Macs, use amd64 architecture
--container-architecture linux/amd64

# Disable container daemon socket (fixes podman compatibility)
--container-daemon-socket=-

# Reuse containers between runs for faster iteration
--reuse
